  "worldId": "forest",
  "title": "森林入口：发现脚印",
  "rewards": {
    "growthPoints": 5
  },
  "scenes": [
    {
      "sceneId": "gate",
      "background": "assets/story/pixel-worlds-v1/scenes/forest/forest-01.webp",
      "lines": [
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "星门把小小探险家送到森林入口。阳光穿过树叶，地上留下了一串圆圆的脚印。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "这里就是森林入口。我们先把“发现脚印”记在地图上。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "我闻到了叶子和雨水的味道，森林朋友就在附近。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "先听树叶的声音，再用温柔的动作帮助这里的朋友。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "activity",
          "activityType": "scan",
          "prompt": "找出通往森林深处的脚印。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "right",
          "actions": [
            {
              "label": "观察圆脚印",
              "feedback": "脚印通向一棵大树。"
            },
            {
              "label": "看看树叶路牌",
              "feedback": "叶子轻轻摇动，指向溪边。"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "narration",
          "text": "小小探险家完成了第一步，观察圆脚印让周围的线索变得清楚起来。",
          "character": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "看！刚才藏起来的线索露出来了。",
          "character": "hero",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "轻轻完成这一步，藏在叶影里的小路出现了。",
          "character": "pet",
          "position": "right"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "把这条小路和森林地图连起来，萤光就会为我们领路。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "记住这片叶子的形状，下一次遇见它就知道该往哪里走。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "left"
        },
        {
          "type": "dialogue",
          "text": "认识‘森’字，就像看见很多树站在一起。",
          "character": "forest_guide",
          "position": "right"
        }
      ],
      "sceneAssets": {
